works.description: Here is one neat little boat your rich little kid could steer in the backyard. The Woody-Cart is a push-powered ride-on vehicle for children up to four years old. The basic idea behind the Woody-Cart was to build a high class, timeless designer piece that is liked by children and parents alike. The stunning push-powered has been engineered in the basis of photographs and vintage paintings of the mahogany wood boat classics of the ‘50s. The Woody-Cart is made in the style of classic wooden motor boats such as those of Riva, Chris Craft or Boesch.
